  (text "We use a 2x10 female pin socket as it fits perfectly in a 2x8\nshrouded pin header on the host side. We don't use a 2x8 \npin socket as it is narrower than a 2x8 shrouded header \nand can allowing off-by-1 pin insertion. We don't use a 2x8 \nkeyed pin sockets are they seem to be very uncommon."
    (at 249.555 47.625 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.4986 1.4986)) (justify left bottom))
    (uuid e7512d6a-3a77-45fa-9913-f60a9f972df2)
  )
